
Computes a csv filee containing a list of mathematicians with birth and death data.
Each mathematician is associated with the number of links coming from other mathematician pages (N_LINKS).
N_LINKS can serve as a celebrity indicator.

Installation
------------
Install PECL extension php-yaml :
sudo apt install php-yaml

Preparation
------------
- Copy config.yml.dist to config.yml
- Adapt the paths to your local machine


Execution
------------
In a console, from current directory (containing this README) :

Retrieve pages containing the biographies on your local machine :
php run/step1.php

Retrieve pages containing the places on your local machine :
php run/step2.php

Generate csv :
php run/step3.php


Execution result :
------------

step 1
permits to retrieve 2842 persons

step 2
permits to retrieve birthplaces except for 166 mathematicians
(1269 birthplaces)

step 3
see build/stats.php


Examine result
------------
php build/stats.php


